{"tid":2231091,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《福布斯》公布2020全球最高收入女星排名","createTime":"2020-10-05T11:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T12:22:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07233abd5bb9e8422902a903016c1adbdbd3cf98","tid":2231091,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"財經雜誌《福布斯》日前公布2020全球最掙錢女星排名，蘇菲亞維格拉（Sofia Vergara）以《摩登家庭》最終一季及擔任《全美一叮》評審，年掙4300萬美元（約3.35億港元），踢走去年居首位的《黑寡婦》史嘉麗祖安遜（Scarlett Johansson），成為冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n正在拍Marvel電影《永恆族》的安祖蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie），則以3350萬美元（約2.6億港元）位列亞軍。<br />\n<br />\n第3位是《神奇女俠》姬兒加杜（Gal Gadot），年掙3150萬美元（約2.4億港元）。<br />\n至於第4至10位依次為<br />\n《凸務Madam》瑪莉莎麥卡菲（Melissa McCarthy）<br />\n《洗錢天堂網絡》梅麗史翠普（Meryl Streep）<br />\n《無聲絕境2》愛美莉賓特（Emily Blunt）<br />\n《小謊言》妮歌潔曼（Nicole Kidman）<br />\n《醫人當自強》愛倫龐彼奧（Ellen Pompeo）<br />\n《使女的故事》伊莉莎白莫斯（Elisabeth Moss）<br />\n《剋&middot;寡婦》維奧拉戴維斯（Viola Davis）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20201005/s00016/1601835460142/%E3%80%8A%E6%91%A9%E7%99%BB%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E3%80%8B%E8%98%87%E8%8F%B2%E4%BA%9E%E7%B6%AD%E6%A0%BC%E6%8B%89%E8%86%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%90%B8%E9%87%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20201005%2Fs00016%2F1601835460142%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2591%25A9%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%258F%25B2%25E4%25BA%259E%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%2586%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2590%25B8%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2598%259F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=fb70ae77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20201005%2Fs00016%2F1601835460142%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2591%25A9%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%258F%25B2%25E4%25BA%259E%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25A